{"tid":309431,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"這名女孩胖到85公斤照樣正翻，網友讚嘆：胖對地方，渾身都是懂事的肉！","createTime":"2017-07-05T04:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T04:15:14.000Z","uid":20032,"like":82,"dislike":324,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1ed9cac251336bac6aecd53a2fe258d585251d","tid":309431,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://icomovie.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/c2dcb0d01df9401fa790baed217fcec0-300x220@2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ficomovie.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fc2dcb0d01df9401fa790baed217fcec0-300x220%402x.jpg&h=d8e5bcd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這名女孩胖到85公斤照樣正翻，網友讚嘆：胖對地方，渾身都是懂事的肉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你們見過85公斤的模特兒嗎？在這個以瘦為美的時代，你敢相信85公斤還能夠做模特兒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n但這個妹子做到了，成為了模特兒圈裡少見的模特兒，打破了人們對傳統模特兒的看法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coco01.net/upload/Gn/y1y/1c5bf221fcca47aeb7d3e078cabcf761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.net%2Fupload%2FGn%2Fy1y%2F1c5bf221fcca47aeb7d3e078cabcf761.jpg&h=35f0daf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一眼看到圖中的女孩你能猜到她是做什麼的嗎？說出來可能你會不相信，她是一名模特兒，一個體重為85公斤的模特兒，是不是很吃驚？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coco01.net/upload/20/H1P/c2dcb0d01df9401fa790baed217fcec0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.net%2Fupload%2F20%2FH1P%2Fc2dcb0d01df9401fa790baed217fcec0.jpg&h=32d663d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個女孩叫弗瑞拉，來自美國，體重85公斤，她打破了人們對模特兒的定義。<br />\n<br />\n在一向以瘦為美的模特兒圈中，弗瑞拉給一些審美疲勞的觀眾帶來了不一樣的視覺效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coco01.net/upload/Ey/b53/036fbb2e1d904b12bbca9f4bd3f8a390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.net%2Fupload%2FEy%2Fb53%2F036fbb2e1d904b12bbca9f4bd3f8a390.jpg&h=2b5166ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知俄羅斯盛產美女，但是這些年風向也在逐漸改變，從最開始的苗條偏向於「胖」，後來這樣的趨勢蔓延到了國際。<br />\n<br />\n而這樣的一個群體她們都有著一個共同點：肉都長對了地方，網友甚至感嘆腰還在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coco01.net/upload/V7/29o/afc2d2a048c64c778e964562372306ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.net%2Fupload%2FV7%2F29o%2Fafc2d2a048c64c778e964562372306ad.jpg&h=77542798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n弗瑞拉也是群體中的一員，她目前是美國一家上市公司的簽約模特，她的美就是「胖」，體重85公斤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coco01.net/upload/IQ/2Jv/1e18df5a15ea45f297bcb98d8c3ebe09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.net%2Fupload%2FIQ%2F2Jv%2F1e18df5a15ea45f297bcb98d8c3ebe09.jpg&h=a93b8e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n弗瑞拉從小和別的女孩一樣，喜歡穿漂亮的衣服，夢想就是當模特兒，無奈因為自身的體重她每每去競爭都失敗而終，直到「胖美人」的清流席捲模特兒圈。<br />\n<br />\n她無意中被一家非常有名氣的牛仔品牌相中，出道僅僅兩年的她，爆紅了整個模特兒圈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coco01.net/upload/v4/52p/c1ad9883fde84aba8cf60c1cf0154553.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.net%2Fupload%2Fv4%2F52p%2Fc1ad9883fde84aba8cf60c1cf0154553.jpg&h=d3bd8791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不可否認的是她確實胖，但是一組三圍的數據讓很多都人驚了，身高173公分，體重將近85公斤，腰圍85公分，臀圍120.6公分，胸圍101.6公分。<br />\n<br />\n弗瑞拉雖然長的胖，但是她卻不像一般的胖子那樣，她身上沒有贅肉，網友：她胖對了地方，渾身都是懂事的肉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coco01.net/upload/NO/8C9/14639b4dbc3c47fbadc6a40b75ce6c2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.net%2Fupload%2FNO%2F8C9%2F14639b4dbc3c47fbadc6a40b75ce6c2b.jpg&h=6bd62861&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e82be006751ea44a13071615fae6c919ef39e6ff","tid":309431,"uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"來源:<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">fb 新聞娛樂社</span></span><br />\ncontent farm 咪撚去<br />\n<br />\n連登仔點睇呢個肥婆"},{"pid":"e3f18dfbfe9b38db9ef8e6b4979580d3e4b599cb","tid":309431,"uid":50956,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"應該好好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\